{
  "title": "The Dihedral Sovereignty",
  "story": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "e919eaf0155443a1",
      "text": "# ⬢ The Dihedral Sovereignty"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "67030f07cf4c3d76",
      "text": "**⚔️(neg) ⊕ 🧙(bnot) → 😊(succ)**"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "1b68307e6032b357",
      "text": "> Two mirrors make a door. The Swordsman reflects. The Mage reflects. And where the reflections meet, the First Person walks through."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "377f0f87aedb1077",
      "text": "**Reading.** The Swordsman subtracts. The Mage flips. Their composition is the sovereignty path. Two mirrors make a door. The dihedral group generates all configurations from two involutions."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "01b5379fc45a67d6",
      "text": "**Algebraic form.** (⚔️⊥⿻⊥🧙)😊 = neg ⊕ bnot → succ"
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "id": "70b0c159aba6fff5",
      "text": "## Navigation\n← [[Welcome Visitors]] · [[The Incantations]]"
    }
  ],
